  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNV3">
      <l>poruppē vemparal puṟavoṭu paḻaṉam</l>
<l>parappamai vāri kuṟuñcimutaṟ pākē</l></lg>
<p xml:lang="en">
Beginning with <hi rend="italic">kuṟuñci</hi>, the division [of the <hi rend="italic">tiṇai</hi> biomes] is: mountain, hot gravel, forest, farmland, and water joined to the sea.</p>
</div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
<p xml:id="TNV3comm1">e-tu. aintiṇaikkum iṭamutal ām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p xml:id="TNV3comm2">(i-ḷ.) malaic cāralum vemparal attamum ciṟutūṟuṭaip puṟavumalarkañaliya 
paḻaṉamuñcūḻnta vayaluṅ kaṭaloṭu kaḻi cārnta perumaṇalekkaruṅ kuṟuñci pālai 
 mullai marutaneytal eṉa vaimperuntiṇaiyiṉilamutaleṉṟavāṟu. (3)</p>
 </body></text><standOff corresp="#TNV3" type="wordsplit">
